# Agent Information: Professional Qualification in Entrepreneurship - Demonstration Project

## Project Overview
This directory contains all deliverables for the entrepreneur vocational qualification demonstration exam project.

## Important Deadline
- **Assessment Date**: February 18, 2026 (18.2.2026)
- **Time**: 13:30â€“14:30
- **Location**: PSK Adult Education Center

## Required Components Completed
The following competency areas have been completed as part of the required "Mandatory Parts of the Qualification":

1. **Working in Business Operations (30 cr)**
   - Assessment form filled out
   - Practical business operations documented

2. **Planning and Starting Business Operations (60 cr)**
   - Comprehensive business plan (Business Plan)
   - Financial calculations (YT4/YT5)
   - Responsibility plan (Sustainability Plan)

## Deliverables in This Directory
- Business plan for DummyMusicCompany
- Financial projections and calculations
- Completed assessment forms
- Marketing materials with visual prompts
- Responsibility plan addressing sustainability
- Completion summary

## Preparation Status
All required materials have been prepared and organized for the assessment. The project is ready for the February 18th evaluation.
